features: Not all wipes are created equal. Dr. Talbot's Soothing Baby Wipes are gentle on your child’s delicate skin with naturally inspired ingredients like Chamomile, Aloe, and Calendula.
Formulated to provide the ultimate soft and gentle care. Dr. Talbot's Soothing Baby Wipes are free of alcohols, parabens, and fragrances. No ethanol or drying alcohol.
For those big messes, reach for Dr. Talbot’s Soothing Baby Wipes. These wipes are extra thick, pre-moistened cleansing wipes with Citroganix for those heavy-duty cleaning jobs.
Dr. Talbot’s Soothing Baby Wipes are extra soft, making them ideal for newborns. Our soft wipes are also strong, offering a complete clean from top to bottom.
Be prepared for life’s little boo-boos at or away from home. Dr. Talbot’s Soothing Baby Wipes come in a 64-count pack convenient for travel.
The convenient resealable package is ideal for purses and diaper bags. Seal after each use to guarantee your wipes stay moist and ready for use while your bag stays dry.
body.description: Nuby soothing baby wipes clean and moisturize baby's most sensitive skin. The wipes are ultra thick and strong, yet soft and gentle to the touch. Made without any parabens, alcohol, chlorine, formaldehydes, or harsh chemicals, you can be sure your baby is getting the best.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Our Philosophy At Dr. Talbot's, we believe in offering safe, natural, and effective solutions possible for the whole family. We believe in harnessing natural ingredients so infants and parents can turn to mother nature's solutions. In honor of legendary pediatrician Dr. Ralph Jefferson Talbot, who developed America's trusted diaper rash ointment formula in 1933, Dr. Talbot's is committed to continuing the tradition of caring for loved ones.
